lead_paragraph: WARHEIT--Walter S. On Behalf of the Officers and employees of Gutterman's, Inc., Funeral Directors of New York and Gutterman Warheit Memorial Chapel of Florida, we announce the passing, and mourn the loss of our associate of over 50 years. 1/3
